title: Perth remitter registration not renewed (AUSTRAC - Australian Transaction Reports and Analysis Centre)
text: ( Source : AUSTRAC - Australian Transaction Reports and Analysis Centre ) AUSTRAC has not renewed the registration of Global Forex ( Perth ) Pty Ltd as an independent remittance dealer on the Remittance Sector Register , meaning it is now illegal
